snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple Character 2000 Series Vol 02 - Afro Inu - The Puzzle (2001)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Afro Inu: The Puzzle is a Puzzle game, developed by Axes Art Amuse and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2001.
